    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So if most experts see it as \"crucial,\" does that mean the arguments against it—like the impact on working-class people who can't easily switch to transit—are considered less scientifically or practically valid in these planning discussions?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
